response.overview: Boog, a domesticated 900lb. Grizzly bear finds himself stranded in the woods 3 days before Open Season. Forced to rely on Elliot, a fast-talking mule deer, the two form an unlikely friendship and must quickly rally other forest animals if they are to form a rag-tag army against the hunters.
response.tagline: All Fur One. One Fur All.
response.title: Open Season

results.name: Open Season (2006) The Voices Behind The Stars
